# Puppeteer Configuration / Configuraci칩n de Puppeteer
#
# PUPPETEER_SKIP_DOWNLOAD is an environment variable that tells Puppeteer
# to skip downloading Chromium (~300MB) during npm install.
#
# PUPPETEER_SKIP_DOWNLOAD es una variable de entorno que le indica a Puppeteer
# que omita la descarga de Chromium (~300MB) durante npm install.
#
# This project uses jsreport-chrome-pdf which depends on puppeteer, but uses
# the system's Chrome instead of the bundled one.
#
# Este proyecto usa jsreport-chrome-pdf que depende de puppeteer, pero usa
# el Chrome del sistema en lugar del incluido.
#
# How to set / C칩mo configurarlo:
#
# Linux/Mac:
#   export PUPPETEER_SKIP_DOWNLOAD=true
#   npm install
#
# Windows (PowerShell):
#   $env:PUPPETEER_SKIP_DOWNLOAD = "true"
#   npm install
#
# Or add to your shell profile permanently / O agregar permanentemente al perfil:
#   echo 'export PUPPETEER_SKIP_DOWNLOAD=true' >> ~/.bashrc
#
# Note: The old config option "puppeteer_skip_download" in .npmrc is deprecated
# Nota: La opci칩n antigua "puppeteer_skip_download" en .npmrc est치 obsoleta
